        "faq_item_y7kM8h": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Returns",
            "answer": "<p>We understand there are some differences between an online and an in-store shopping experience, which is why there are a few slight variations in the way we handle returns and exchanges for both.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_qwM6LU": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "IN-STORE PURCHASES & RETURNS",
            "answer": "<p>If your product has a defect or technical fault, you must return it back to our head office within 30 days. Please return items in original condition and with all tags still attached. We understand circumstances can change, if you change your mind after an in-store purchase, we can offer a full credit note or exchange of an equivalent item.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_V96nAy": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "ONLINE PURCHASES & RETURNS",
            "answer": "<p>We understand that purchasing a tailored garment online can be tricky, subsequently, we offer a full refund in the event of a change of mind.</p><p>For a return or an exchange, online orders have to be sent back to our head office within 30 days from the date of purchase. After we have received your return, you can expect to receive your refund within 14 days. This will be sent to the same method you used to pay.</p><p>Once your return has been processed, you will receive a confirmation email.<br/><br/>To request a return or exchange, don't forget to fill out and include our \"returns & exchanges\" form when sending a product back to us. Postage costs are not covered.<br/><br/>You can download the form from here: <a href=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0898/1859/5696/files/Peter-Jackson-Returns-form.pdf?v=1750907363\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0898/1859/5696/files/Peter-Jackson-Returns-form.pdf?v=1750907363\">Download</a></p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_NkEHfM": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "HIGH VOLUME ORDERS",
            "answer": "<p>Due to high demand and increased order volume, our warehouse team are experiencing delays in dispatching orders. Please allow for extended dispatch times and extra delivery time due to the high volume.<br/><br/>Peter Jackson uses third party couriers and delivery times are subject to their service capacity. Unfortunately, this is beyond our control. Our delivery time frame is estimated only and Peter Jackson will not be held liable for any loss, expense, or damage caused by dispatch or delivery delays.<br/><br/>We sincerely appreciate your patience and understanding.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_PkewJK": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "SHIPPING METHODS",
            "answer": "<p><strong>All orders take on average 1-3 business days to process before shipping</strong></p><p>Standard Domestic Shipping - $10 (Free on orders over $99)</p><ul><li>Melbourne Metro: 1-3 business days</li><li>Other capitals: 3-5 business days</li><li>Regional: 5-7 business days</li></ul><p>Express Shipping - $15</p><ul><li>Major cities: 1-2 business days (guaranteed)</li><li>Regional: 3-4 business days</li></ul><p>Tracking is provided for Australian orders only.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_PkgiDe": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING",
            "answer": "<p>International orders are placed in local currency. Shipping is free for all international orders. </p><p>Dispatch times vary depending on local carriers. </p><p><strong>Countries we currently ship international orders to: </strong></p><ul><li>China</li><li>France</li><li>Germany</li><li>Hong Kong</li><li>India</li><li>Indonesia</li><li>Ireland</li><li>Italy</li><li>Japan</li><li>Lithuania</li><li>Malaysia</li><li>Netherlands</li><li>New Zealand</li><li>Pakistan</li><li>Philippines</li><li>Singapore</li><li>Spain</li><li>Sweden</li><li>Thailand</li><li>United Kingdom</li><li>United States</li><li>Vietnam</li></ul><p><strong>We specifically deliver DDP (Delivered Duty Paid).</strong> This means there are no hidden costs when you receive your items. </p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_PkgAkA": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "STOCK AVAILABILITY",
            "answer": "<p>Our stock levels change frequently and there may be some garments only available online for a limited time. If the size you are after is not available online, simply contact our Customer Service team (03 9415 6281) and they will do their best to track the right size down for you.</p><p>There may also be times when a garment purchased via our website is not available in our online warehouse when we come to dispatch. In this case, we will do our best to source the garment from one of our stores and email you about this within one working day of your order.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_A77NFn": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "GENERAL QUESTIONS",
            "answer": "<p><strong>What payment methods are available?<br/><br/></strong>We accept all major credit cards in-store and online. We also accept payments through Paypal for online purchases and Afterpay for in-store and online purchases. Visa, Mastercard and Amex have a small transaction percentage attached.</p><p><br/><strong>How can I search for items on the website?</strong><br/><br/>Click on the magnifying glass icon on the top-right of your screen. You can start typing a product code (SKU) if it’s known to you, or a colour, pattern, product style, etc. e.g: grey check jacket.</p><p><br/><strong>Can I hire a suit?</strong><br/><br/>Unfortunately, we do not offer hiring services.</p><p><br/><strong>How can I order online?</strong><br/><br/>Once you’ve found a product you like, you can select the size and quantity from the product page and click “add to cart”. It will give you the option to keep shopping, or head straight to check-out, where you’ll have to enter your shipping address and select a payment method.</p><p><br/>You can log in with your email and password if you already have an online account. It will assist with a faster checkout process.</p><p><br/><strong>How do I know what size I am?</strong><br/><br/>We want you to find the perfect fit, which is why we have a size chart you can access by clicking on the \"What's my size\" link after clicking \"Select size\" on any suit or sports jacket.<br/><br/><strong>Can I change or cancel my order?<br/><br/></strong>Once an order has been placed on our website, it’s not possible to cancel it. However, you might be able to change it if you get in touch with us before it has been dispatched.</p><p><br/><strong>How can I find the nearest Peter Jackson store?</strong><br/><br/>We have over 60 stores throughout the country and have listed them all by state in our store locator. You can access it by clicking on the \"find a store\" link on the top right corner of your screen.<br/><br/><strong>Was my order successful?</strong><br/><br/>If your order was successful you would receive a confirmation email shortly after completing payment. If you haven’t received any confirmation from us, check your spam folder or get in touch with us at <a href=\"mailto:info@peterjacksons.com\" title=\"mailto:info@peterjacksons.com\">info@peterjacksons.com</a></p><p><br/><strong>When will I get my order?</strong><br/><br/>We dispatch all orders within 3 – 5 business days. Generally, standard delivery takes between 3 – 5 business from the date of dispatch. Check our Shipping Information page <a href=\"https://www.peterjacksons.com/pages/shipping-delivery\" target=\"_self\">here</a> for more information.<br/><br/><strong>How can I track my order?</strong><br/><br/>Right after dispatch, you will receive an email from us with a confirmation and a tracking number for Australia Post.</p><p><strong>I didn't receive a confirmation email for my order, did it go through?</strong><br/><br/>Check your spam folder. If you haven’t received a confirmation from us 24 hours after placing your order, contact us at <a href=\"mailto:info@peterjacksons.com\" title=\"mailto:info@peterjacksons.com\">info@peterjacksons.com</a> or <a href=\"tel:+0394156281\">(03) 9415 6281</a><br/><br/><strong>My order arrived but it’s incomplete<br/><br/></strong>In some cases, we dispatch an order in separate parcels due to the stock’s availability at the time. If you experience this, allow some extra time for the rest of the order to arrive. You can also contact us to inquire about the current status of your order.</p>"
          }
        }
